carrots this time around,

00:02:00.208 --> 00:02:02.915
as well as some of the blueberries,

00:02:02.915 --> 00:02:04.874
and then I'm gonna finish
off with something that has

00:02:04.874 --> 00:02:07.882
a lot of juice, like an apple, and start.

00:02:07.882 --> 00:02:12.771
(juicer grinding)

00:02:20.541 --> 00:02:24.890
(juicer winding down)

00:02:24.890 --> 00:02:27.782
